  fhir:description [ fhir:v "This Resource includes all the people and organizations who plan to participate in the coordination and delivery of care for a patient.\n\nCareteam represents department and practitioner (doctor/staff) assigned to the Patient in ARIA.\n\nARIA does not configure predefined teams, so single Careteam per Patient will represent associations with Department and practitioner."] ; # 
