       fhir:comment [ fhir:v "\n* List of Validations of members:\n\n    *  Hospital\n        * 1. Default Hospital is mandatory.\n        * 2. Only one Hospital can be set as Default Hospital.\n\n    *  Department\n        * 1. If no primary departments is provided in payload then default hospital's one department gets assigned as primary department.\n        * 2. Only one Department can be set as Default Department.\n        * 3. New onBehalfOf field has been introduced for department participant which will have a reference to the associated Organization(Hospital) in ARIA. (Supported only on ARIA V18 or onwards)\n\n    *  Practitioner\n        * 1. Only one Oncologist can be set as Primary Oncologist per hospital in CareTeam.\n        * 2. New onBehalfOf field has been introduced for oncologist, primary oncologist or staff participant which will have a reference to the associated Organization(Hospital) in ARIA. (Supported only on ARIA V18 or onwards)\n        * 3. Only one Physician can be set as Primary Physician in CareTeam.\n" ] ;
